The output of this process will be a histogram showing the distribution of division times, which directly addresses your requirement for visualizing the time it takes for cells to divide. This histogram can provide valuable insights into the cell division process within your time-lapse microscopy video, enabling you to understand the temporal aspects of cell division more deeply.

